# Build-context hygiene for repo-root image builds (apps/backend, sandbox images).
# Keep package/app SOURCE; drop heavy or irrelevant trees so the context stays small.
.git
.github
**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.DS_Store
.claude
